        <abstract>
            <p>Would be delighted to see CVR at Down, but is in precarious health and cannot talk to anyone for more than an hour.</p> 
<p>Wrote to CVR a few weeks ago to thank him for his book [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">7794</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Will expect CVR on Thursday unless he hears otherwise.</p>
        </abstract>
